      "properties": {
        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "Because it hides the hard part. Sustainability is a systems problem \u2014 you cannot optimize one part without moving another. Fix emissions in isolation and you push the cost into water, or land, or t\u2026"
